verbose_text: Currently, both VEGFR3 blocking antibodies (IMC-3C5) and heparanase inhibitors (SST0001, M402, PI-88, and PG545) are in various stages of clinical trial evaluation, and their efficacy with or without standard chemotherapy in large patient cohorts is yet to be determined (http://clinicaltrials.gov).
